snippet.title: Sonic Adventure 2: Super Hard Mode (SAGE 2020)
snippet.description:
This video showcases the new stages in the Super Hard mode mod for Sonic Adventure 2. This was put out for SAGE 2020. The new stages include City Escape, Radical Highway, Aquatic Mine, Security Hall, Eternal Engine, and Lost Colony.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Super Hard Stages mod by "Dry Paratroopa"
